Login - Register

Add funds - Withdraw funds

80 - 20 rule
when fund is added - 80% goes to spendings + 20% goes to savings

when fund is withdrawn - reduced from spending

transfer - transfers money from savings to spending or spending to savings


DB Schema :-
User - built-in
transactions - user, amount, reason, date, time
Funds - user, spendables, savings

Urls :-
/login/
/logout/
/register/
/
/transactions/
/add/
/withdraw/
/tranasfer/
/404/
/invalid-request/

views :-
login - POST GET
logout
register - POST GET
home
transactions
add - POST
withdraw - POST
tranasfer